-- 084_topograf_services.sql
-- Topograph/ANCPI/OCPI cadastral service catalog (groups A+B from the cfunciara
-- competitor analysis). Each is a manually-fulfilled service: the collaborator
-- (topograph) obtains the document at OCPI/BCPI and uploads the scanned PDF via
-- the /colaborator portal, which auto-delivers it to the customer.
--
-- All reuse the existing PropertyDataStep (zero React changes). Group A searches
-- by property (CF/cadastral); group B enables identification by owner.
--
-- base_price values are PLACEHOLDERS — admin-editable at /admin/settings →
-- Servicii, pending Mircea's real price list. Idempotent on slug.
-- config + lawyer_fee_ron use table defaults ('{}' / 0).

